<br>
Surely absor can't find fault with that. Just because it resembles something an evil necro does diminishes in meaning when one considers that the line between good and evil in everyone, according to some, is thinly etched and precarious at best. So certainly, the &quot;Good Wizard,&quot; in his search for more magical force would delve into those shady recesses of his pysche when in a Hermetic Transformation. <br>
<br>
On a lighter note, many people think Wizzies a bunch of KSers anyway.....even in the error of their ways the masses have marked us with an &quot;evil&quot; taint. If that is to be, then at least let us share something in common with our brethren Necros and restore our mana from our physical essense. <br>
<br>
Goanad<br>
